{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850349320,"sessionID":"ses_287134055ffecuXkUAiE6OpdKT","part":{"id":"prt_d78ede02c001c6QlfM7ekHb1fD","messageID":"msg_d78edccf2001BpKbqXrBdCs8IG","sessionID":"ses_287134055ffecuXkUAiE6OpdKT","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_a78d8c70395340c9b6fd6110","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-012 ŌĆö õ╝ÜĶ»ØÕŁśÕé©µÄźÕÅŻÕ«Üõ╣ē\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing session storage interface in `pkg/store`.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-012\n10: - **Module**: `pkg/store`\n11: - **Language**: Go\n12: - **Size**: S\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Background\n17: \n18: \n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## Requirement: Session Storage Interface\n23: \n24: ### Scenario: \n25: \n26: **GIVEN** \n27: **WHEN** \n28: **THEN** \n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ## Acceptance Criteria\n33: \n34: - [ ] \n35: \n36: ---\n37: \n38: ## References\n39: \n40: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md`\n\n(End of file - total 40 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-012 ŌĆö õ╝ÜĶ»ØÕŁśÕé©µÄźÕÅŻÕ«Üõ╣ē\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing session storage interface in `pkg/store`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-012\n- **Module**: `pkg/store`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n\n\n---","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-012/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775850349299,"end":1775850349317}}}}
